OL,14,Fnewspaper reported on Wednesday
OL,15,Fmorning that the pledge was under
OL,16,Freview, or could face delay, amid
OL,17,Ffears the higher cost of employing
OL,18,Fyoung people could put off firms from
OL,19,Fhiring them.
